{"tid":504894,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【調查】近8成人差200萬先退到休","createTime":"2017-12-20T14:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T05:01:16.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7b235e88a8d0502cde17a702e6305d7cfc722cfd","tid":504894,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:04:00.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171220/large/1513747878_748c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171220%2Flarge%2F1513747878_748c.jpg&h=6e2e8f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有調查發現，77%受訪者未儲夠錢退休，平均差200萬。<br />\n<br />\n香港投資基金公會公布調查，訪問了575名受訪者，指以退休年齡61歲計，要維持退休前的生活水平，指需要至少310萬元，但有77%受訪者僅儲約120萬元，<br />\n有近6成半受訪者表示，將考慮調查生活質素，例如減少每月開支、減少旅遊等。<br />\n公會行政總裁黃王慈明表示，單靠強積金，明顯不足以退休，鼓勵一定要「做多啲」，包括其他投資。<br />\n對於積金局研究容許市民提取強積金作首次置業，她指公會成員普遍不同意，認為違反強積金作退休用途的原意，而且怕因此開先例，屆時可能會出現為子女買樓等各用途。<br />\n記者：張浚浩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171220/57604948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57604948&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7591d05a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57604948&h=58dfbe03\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171220/57604948</a>"},{"pid":"93964a3aece0d779aa96c56c38a71d07c01b4475","tid":504894,"uid":5843,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊"},{"pid":"22ec534c4ad147162c45bb3390ddab7ed6b1c7b1","tid":504894,"uid":40207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n你估做三十年樓按真係要供足三十年?"},{"pid":"dcdffa1e14dbbff1552ee473fc505e50fc8f85c0","tid":504894,"uid":72173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n你估做三十年樓按真係要供足三十年?</blockquote><br />\n點會供足三十年<br />\n到時你要另外再借錢分六十年還"},{"pid":"57208fce45e176d9c9deda987945907a0fd279f5","tid":504894,"uid":40207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n你估做三十年樓按真係要供足三十年?</blockquote><br />\n點會供足三十年<br />\n到時你要另外再借錢分六十年還</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁就唔會有6成半業主係供完，而未供完樓既業主當中 平均供款只係佔收入唔夠兩成"},{"pid":"d5211d1cb827565332ed0c12b9a957e1e2371c7f","tid":504894,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n你估做三十年樓按真係要供足三十年?</blockquote><br />\n點會供足三十年<br />\n到時你要另外再借錢分六十年還</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁就唔會有6成半業主係供完，而未供完樓既業主當中 平均供款只係佔收入唔夠兩成</blockquote><br />\nsource from?"},{"pid":"b6b491ab8d1a097a025242a57388f7ee495453cf","tid":504894,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4830872989d63f0dce2785f17e1c74ebaa4faf1","tid":504894,"uid":40207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我屌你老母啊如果要買樓啊都供到60歲啦仲點儲錢退休啊</blockquote><br />\n你估做三十年樓按真係要供足三十年?</blockquote><br />\n點會供足三十年<br />\n到時你要另外再借錢分六十年還</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁就唔會有6成半業主係供完，而未供完樓既業主當中 平均供款只係佔收入唔夠兩成</blockquote><br />\nsource from?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過去十年，按揭利率偏低，政府又經常寬免差餉，令業主的空置成本大降。由於按揭利率偏低，不少自置居所的業主在過去十年還清供款，沒有按揭供款的自置單位比率由52.2%，上升至去年的65.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/columns/壹角度/20170316/487199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fcolumns%2F%E5%A3%B9%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%2F20170316%2F487199&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4a21e2f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fcolumns%2F%E5%A3%B9%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%2F20170316%2F487199&h=328283dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/columns/壹角度/20170316/487199</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n租住私人住宅單位的家庭住戶的租金中位數為$1萬，其租金與收入比率中位數為30.7%，<br />\n而居於公營租住房屋單位的家庭住戶的相對數字分別為$1500及9.3%。<br />\n同時，居於自置私人永久性房屋而有按揭供款或借貸還款的家庭住戶，其按揭供款及借貸還款中位數為$10,500，與收入比率中位數為19%。<br />\n居於資助自置居所房屋的家庭住戶的相應數字分別為$5,480及15.5%。"},{"pid":"3c8f365c022e287124f3b10c3b5f4f542c9c6e10","tid":504894,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"310萬夠退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我後生玩撚哂d 錢老左做廢老算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒屌下30,40後"},{"pid":"effc572aee8944acdade27972355cbb903d21e32","tid":504894,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"如果公務員根本就唔洗擔心退休生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f59e2a1e6a6469ec4aea56f7a0ee98beb6f840d","tid":504894,"uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果公務員根本就唔洗擔心退休生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新制無長糧喇"},{"pid":"b7b0e0fa64441e46e82276cfe3adbc3b2fdc2ce5","tid":504894,"uid":126312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單靠強積金，明顯不足以退休</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁仲搞黎做咩呀. 每個月cut我$1500逼我買垃圾蝕錢養班廢柴基金佬"},{"pid":"9b179